{
  "stem": "10905.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How could they?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my-- there was a large group on my mother's side who are very, very Hasidic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My grandfather, as I said, was a [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Shamus. ?] We were observant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's just-- [INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's just that-- absolutely, there was no conflict, no animosity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's just that my father always believed in freedom of thought, and freedom of will, and freedom of speech.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a very outspoken man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, he was going to decide what the right thing was for his children, not some rabbi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the war was still on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of course, you couldn't come and go, because you could come and go on the grounds of the hotel, but you couldn't leave because this was-- you-- you were under martial law under Swiss military.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they wouldn't let you leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] you know-- you could not come and go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Again, fortune shined upon us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They needed a German-speaking physician and my father had studied in Berlin, did his residency in Kiel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was fluent in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he became the chief pediatrician of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, the hospital was not under military control, so my sister and I were-- we were the only-- only people who were free to go as we wished.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, we were not going to run away and go any place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we did make friends, some Swiss friends, and-- whom we are still in contact with today, who are here in New York.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- Just very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went, and I learned how to ski.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I skied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had to put our lights out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was a-- there was a black out in Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Even though we were in Switzerland, there was a blackout.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
